                          <img class="img-fluid" src="/img/slide1.jpg" alt=""> 
                      </div>
                      <div class="col-lg-6 mb-0 d-flex align-items-center">
                          <div class="text-align-left align-self-center">
                              <h1 class="h1 text-success"><b>Computer Engineering Department</b> </h1>
                              <h3 class="h2">Learning The Innovation</h3>
                              <p>
                                Our vision is to be the first-ranked Computer Engineering department in the country and achieve international standards in teaching and learning.
                                And, to produce potential graduates who meet the demand of computer engineers with 5 characteristics: creative thinker and good at problem-solving, 
                                self-learner, internationalized, able to work with the team and have good attitude towards team working, moral and ethical.
                              </p>
                          </div>
                      </div>
                  </div>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
              <div class="container">
                  <div class="row p-5">
